OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 17 Mar to Thu 26 Mar
OL,6,FSigns are that much of the UK will see
OL,7,Fa period of more settled weather for
OL,8,Fpart of this period at least. At first
OL,9,Fsome wet and windy weather is likely
OL,10,Facross the northwest especially.
OL,11,FHowever its likely to turn more
OL,12,Fsettled from midweek onwards, and by
OL,13,Fthe weekend most, if not all of the
OL,14,Fcountry should be predominantly dry.
OL,15,FIts possible we could see some
OL,16,Fovernight frost and fog, but by day
OL,17,Fthere should be spells of pleasant
OL,18,Fspring sunshine making it feel warm
OL,19,Faway from coasts exposed to a brisk
OL,20,Feasterly wind. How long the settled
OL,21,Fconditions last is less certain with
OL,22,Fsome signals that showers / rain could
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Freturn later in the period, perhaps
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fthe south most prone to this.
